# compute service where you can upload your code and create lambda functions.it takes care of provisioning and managing the servers that you use to run the code.
 Uses:
  -event driven compute service whwere aws lambda runs your code in response to events. These events could be
   changes to data in aws s3 bucket or an amazon dynamo db
  -compute service to run code in response to HTTp requests using amazon api gateway or api calls made using aws sdks.
 Pricing:
 - Number of requests
   -First1 milion requests are free.$0.20 per 1 million requests
   -Duration
    -chrged from code enters and terminates from lambda,price depends on amount of memory allocated to your 
     your function.
  Features:
  No servers
  Continious scaling
  super cheap
   
  
